{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610/events","html_url":"https://github.com/assertj/assertj/issues/1610","id":496620305,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0OTY2MjAzMDU=","number":1610,"title":"Replace catchThrowable + isInstanceOf(AssertionError.class) by expectAssertionError","user":{"login":"joel-costigliola","id":382613,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4MjYxMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/382613?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola","html_url":"https://github.com/joel-costigliola","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1162167683,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMTYyMTY3Njgz","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/labels/status:%20ideal%20for%20contribution","name":"status: ideal for contribution","color":"C5DEF5","default":false,"description":"An issue that a contributor can help us with"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2019-09-21T06:27:51Z","updated_at":"2024-10-02T23:46:17Z","closed_at":"2019-09-22T06:31:26Z","author_association":"MEMBER","type":{"id":2594686,"node_id":"IT_kwDOASBds84AJ5d-","name":"âš¡Improvement","description":" A general improvement ","color":"blue","created_at":"2024-01-25T19:41:59Z","updated_at":"2025-05-30T17:34:28Z","is_enabled":true},"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"#### Summary\r\n\r\nUse `AssertionsUtil.expectAssertionError` instead of `catchThrowable` + `isInstanceOf(AssertionError.class)` as `expectAssertionError` checks that the caught throwable is an `AssertionError`.\r\n\r\n#### Example\r\n\r\n```java\r\n// WHEN\r\nThrowable throwable = catchThrowable(() -> ...);\r\n// THEN\r\nassertThat(throwable).isInstanceOf(AssertionError.class)\r\n                     .hasMessage(\"error message\");\r\n```\r\nshould be written as\r\n```java\r\n// WHEN\r\nAssertionError assertionError = expectAssertionError(() -> ...);\r\n// THEN\r\nassertThat(assertionError).hasMessage(\"error message\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nLooking for `.isInstanceOf(AssertionError.class)` should be enough to find the code to refactor (it might be quite a lot!)\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"joel-costigliola","id":382613,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4MjYxMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/382613?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola","html_url":"https://github.com/joel-costigliola","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joel-costigliola/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/assertj/assertj/issues/1610/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}